VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (Environment\.getExternalStorageDirectory|Context\.getExternalFilesDir)\s*\(\)\s*\.read
WHEN EXPR MISSING:validate|sanitize|allowlist && MISSING:test|example|sample
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects reading data from external storage without proper input validation.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure External Storage Read.
